magicbook.gtlitecore.api.utils.tuples

类 Pair<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • magicbook.gtlitecore.api.utils.tuples.Pair<K,V>
  • 类型参数:
    K - The type of key.
    V - The type of value.
    所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, BiFunctor<K,V,Pair<?,?>>

    public final class Pair<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements BiFunctor<K,V,Pair<?,?>>, java.io.Serializable
    A functional enhancement of Pair.

    This class is a "pair" structure like Map.Entry, it is suitable for serialization and functional programming operations. For example: 

    
     // Bob is a 24 year old woman.
     Pair<String, Integer> bobAge = Pair.of("Bob", 12)
             .mapKey(String::toLowerCase) // "Bob" -> "bob".
             .mapValue(v -> v * 2); // 12 -> 24.
     // List of all (key, value) => (name, age) ages.
     List<Pair<String, Integer>> ages = Arrays.asList(bobAge);
     // Another convenient operation is transform a pair list to map.
     Map<String, Integer> map = Pair.toMap(ages);
    This structure is an implementation of 2-Functor (BiFunctor).
    作者:
    Magic_Sweepy
    另请参阅:
    序列化表格
